        <h3 class="gem-c-image-card__title">
              <a class="gem-c-image-card__title-link brand__color" href="/government/news/penny-mordaunt-launches-new-funds-to-tackle-period-poverty-globally">Penny Mordaunt launches new funds to tackle period poverty globally</a>
</h3>
      <div class="gem-c-image-card__description"><div class="govspeak">
<p>Ahead of International Women’s Day, Minister for Women and Equalities and Secretary of State for International Development, Penny Mordaunt, will today (4 March) announce a new UK government campaign to break the silence and end period poverty globally by 2030.</p>
</div></div>


